OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fevening with late sunny spells, though
OL,7,Fturning quickly rather chilly. Mainly
OL,8,Fdry for the rest of the night with
OL,9,Fclear spells leading to a risk of
OL,10,Ffrost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FSome sunshine and a frost
OL,13,Ffirst thing in the morning for many.
OL,14,FThe rest of the day will then be dry,
OL,15,Fbright with best of sun along east
OL,16,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
